\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Today we can\'92t answer every question you might have which is why we are opening things up and maybe after today you have a question...\uc0\u8232 \
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 You can go to {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.riverlakechurch.com/"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 \strokec3 www.riverlakechurch.com}}\'a0and ask whatever you want\'85I\'92ll even give you freedom today to send us a message during the sermon\uc0\u8232 \
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 What I do want to do today is spend sometime covering what I see are 5 Lies we do see in scripture that are clear.\uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl1\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 So while we won\'92t make everything clear I hope to clear up a few things that may be confusing or you may have been told wrong.\uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Now, another thing\'85if you\'92re here today and you\'92re not a follower of Jesus we are SO glad you\'92re here. \'a0And I want you to know you don\'92t have to follow any of the things I\'92m going to say. \'a0\uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl1\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
